Vital City Design System
© 2024-2026 Vital City.

This repository contains Vital City's design tokens, components and editorial
guidance. The CSS, HTML and JSON files in this repository are released for
Vital City's own use and for reference by contributors, partners and academic
researchers.

Third-party typefaces referenced here — Halyard Text (Darden Studio), Gascogne
(TypeShop Collection) and Bayard (Vocal Type) — are licensed separately and
are NOT redistributed by this repository. The GascogneTS-Light.ttf file
included in fonts/ is bundled under Vital City's existing license with
TypeShop Collection; if you are not affiliated with Vital City you must obtain
your own license to use it.

The VITAL CITY wordmark and logo are trademarks of Vital City. The wordmark
files in assets/ are provided for contributors producing on-brand Vital City
work and must not be used to imply endorsement or affiliation outside that
context.

Brand guidelines authored by Design for Progress, September 2024.
